These TOS further govern your access to and use of ecobee’s eco+ service (“eco+,” and together with the other web-based or mobile device-based applications provided by ecobee, the “Remote Applications”), whether accessed via an ecobee Product, the ecobee Website, or the ecobee App. Use of eco+ is voluntary. You are under no obligation to use eco+ in order to use any ecobee Services.
